Lady Nyshara, the Woven Empress of Silent Seasons

Lady Nyshara was not born, she was composed, layer by layer, stitch by stitch, from the last silks of forgotten dynasties and the breath of windless winters. Her voice is said to command the rhythm of time in the hidden provinces of the world, where memories bloom like fabric flowers and fade without warning.
